<item>
            <title>[LU-9674] chown fail if nodemap enabled</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9674</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I can not change files owner if  nodemap enabled. Is it correct?&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; chown: changing ownership of &#8216;111&#8217;: Operation not permitted&lt;/p&gt;


</description>
